{"tid":971363,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好憎陸運會既lunch time","createTime":"2019-01-06T14:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T16:23:13.000Z","uid":34489,"like":22,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5ab415135dd6b7c152074e57e24509a4015c7ddc","tid":971363,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:36:57.000Z","msg":"就快就陸運會 仲記得上年陸運會lunch time果陣 <br />\n<br />\n大家一堆堆朋友咁出去搵餐廳食飯 我就一個人行黎行去禁手機又要扮等緊朋友黎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後仲要好辛苦咁搵間冇乜同校學生去既餐廳食飯 因為好怕比人見到自己一個係到食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上年我就專登坐taxi坐左10分鐘左右 離個會場都有一後距離 諗住唔會撞到人 <br />\n<br />\n點知入到間餐廳 就撞正成堆老師 連埋我2個班主任都係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其中一個班主任就問:咦 你黎到咁遠食既? 我地都係渣車黎炸喎 <br />\n<br />\n我: 係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上網check過喱間出名啊麻 <br />\n<br />\n佢:係咩? 我未聽過喎 我地都係是但揀 近會場果邊滿哂人啊 冇計啦..係呢 你一個人? <br />\n<br />\n我:唔係..我朋友黎緊..(當然係老吹架啦) <br />\n<br />\n之後我就即刻打比我個best friend叫佢坐taxi黎 我話請埋佢車錢同飯錢 但佢都唔肯 <br />\n<br />\n我唯有趁班老師傾緊計果陣就叫左個外賣坐車番會場到食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第2日陸運會我連番都冇番tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗番起真係好慘...點解上天要咁對毒撚...唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e3dc1feb386bd07f87c9cc52d7e9d49375a736","tid":971363,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5707c6b22d75cfb5054db6120b022ab16979dd21","tid":971363,"uid":34489,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:42:30.000Z","msg":"諗起D濕尻prefect同埋咩社長D面口真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},